# 🚀 AI Resume Analyzer & Job Intelligence System

An AI-powered Resume Analyzer and ATS Optimization platform built using **Flask, NLP, RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation), Vector Search, and LLM Integration**.

This project helps users:

* Analyze resumes intelligently
* Compare resumes against job descriptions
* Detect missing skills
* Improve ATS compatibility
* Get AI-generated suggestions
* Perform semantic document understanding using RAG

